## dsfHOF variable

Higher order version of [dsf](./dsp.dsf.md) oscillator with pre-configured params. Slightly faster, but not dynamically changeable waveform.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
dsfHOF: (alpha?: number, beta?: number) => StatelessOscillator
```
